image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">Rigtig flot indsats, med mange l&oslash;b op og ned af banen ogs&aring; god til at holde p&aring; bolden, gode afleveringer</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">Angriber/forsvar : Yossi&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">Fysisk st&aelig;rk rigtig sv&aelig;r at tage bolden fra, t&aelig;t p&aring; at scorer flere gange, ogs&aring; god til at spille i forsvaret&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">Allround: Jonatan S (Finland)</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">Blev brugt p&aring; alle pladser, gjorde en rigtig fin indsats</span><br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style="color:#444444"><img src="{SYSVAR:MEDIA_REL}/pgt/2015/IMG_6063.jpg" width="650" height="433" alt="" /><br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style="color:#444444"><span style="background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">K&aelig;re alle spillere,</span><br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style="color:#444444"><span style="background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">Tak for en fantastisk indsats over hele linjen, i kan godt v&aelig;re stolte over jeres pr&aelig;station, dejligt at se jeres gode sammenhold p&aring; og udenfor banen, h&aring;ber vi ses n&aelig;ste &aring;r, god sommer og endnu engang tillykke med guldmedaljerne&nbsp;</span></span></div>\r\n<div><span style="color:#444444"><br />\r\n<span style="background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">Bedste hilsner</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">J&oslash;rgen Henriksen&nbsp;</span></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;<img src="{SYSVAR:MEDIA_REL}/pgt/2015/IMG_5774.jpg" width="650" height="433" alt="" /></div>', '<p>&nbsp;<img src="{SYSVAR:MEDIA_REL}/pgt/2015/B03.jpg" width="650" height="519" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p><em>St&aring;ende: J&oslash;rgen Henriksen, Jossi, Noah, Adam, Jonathan G</em></p>\r\n<p><em>Siddende: Jacob TH, Jacob E, Jacob S, Jonathan S (Helsinki)</em></p>\r\n<p><em>Liggende: Benjamin</em></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><span style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">Holdet bestod af 9 spillere heraf 1 spiller fra Finland.</span><span style="color:#444444"><br />\r\n<span style="background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">Resultater:&nbsp; Torsdag&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">Kamp 1 : Cph vs Oslo/G&oslash;teborg</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">Vi vandt kampen 5-2</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">Kamp 2 : Cph vs Stockholm</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">Vi vandt kampen 6-2</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">Resultater : Fredag</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">Kamp 3 : Cph vs Oslo/G&oslash;teborg</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">Vi vandt kampen 4-2</span><br />\r\n<br 