background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">H&oslash;jre back: Jacob E</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">Sikker bagerst mand med mange gode indgreb i spillet, lavet finalens bedste m&aring;l fra midten af banen med venstre sk&oslash;jten.</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">Venstre back: Jonathan G</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">Meget sikker bagerst mand, god til at flytte spillet op af banen, gode asist,lavet ogs&aring; nogle flotte m&aring;l</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">Midtbanen: Jakob TH</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">Holdets styrmand fremragende til at fordele spillet, gode afleveringer lavet&nbsp; ogs&aring; nogle gode m&aring;l&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">H&oslash;jre wing: Adam&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">Dygtig dribler, med et fremragende venstreben god til at v&aelig;re p&aring; rette sted p&aring; det rigtige tidspunkt, scorede mange af vores m&aring;l&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">Venstre ving : Noah&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">God fysik, meget sv&aelig;r at tage bolden fra, med mange afleveringer der gav m&aring;l, lavet ogs&aring; nogle flotte m&aring;l</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">Angriber/midt: Jacob S</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">Rigtig flot indsats, med mange l&oslash;b op og ned af banen ogs&aring; god til at holde p&aring; bolden, gode afleveringer</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">Angriber/forsvar : Yossi&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">Fysisk st&aelig;rk rigtig sv&aelig;r at tage bolden fra, t&aelig;t p&aring; at scorer flere gange, ogs&aring; god til at spille i forsvaret&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">Allround: Jonatan S (Finland)</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">Blev brugt p&aring; alle pladser, gjorde en rigtig fin indsats</span><br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style="color:#444444"><img src="{SYSVAR:MEDIA_REL}/pgt/2015/IMG_6063.jpg" width="650" height="433" alt="" /><br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style="color:#444444"><span style="background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">K&aelig;re alle spillere,</span><br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style="color:#444444"><span style="background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">Tak for en fantastisk indsats over hele linjen, i kan godt v&aelig;re stolte over jeres pr&aelig;station, dejligt at se jeres gode sammenhold p&aring; og udenfor banen, h&aring;ber vi ses n&aelig;ste &aring;r, god sommer og endnu engang tillykke med guldmedaljerne&nbsp;</span></span></div>\r\n<div><span style="color:#444444"><br />\r\n<span style="background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">Bedste hilsner</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">J&oslash;rgen Henriksen&nbsp;</span></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;<img src="{SYSVAR:MEDIA_REL}/pgt/2015/IMG_5774.jpg" width="650" height="433" alt="" /></div>'),
(206, 206, '<p>&nbsp;<img src="{SYSVAR:MEDIA_REL}/pgt/2015/B07.jpg" width="650" height="471" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p><em>St&aring;ende: Itamar, Isaac, Alon, Samuel SH, Elias A</em></p>\r\n<p><em>Siddende: Gabriel, Joel, Tobias, David, Samuel K</em></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 8.5pt;">Siden PGT-succesen sidste &aring;r i G&oslash;teborg, har Hakoahs U8 drenge arbejdet m&aring;lrettet i deres forberedelse frem mod PGT Oslo 2015. Der er blevet tr&aelig;net, spillet kampe og dyrket venskaber for at st&aring; st&aelig;rkest muligt i kampen&nbsp;om det store trof&aelig;. Det har helet &aring;ret&nbsp;ligget i drengenes baghoveder, at der skulle k&aelig;mpes for at f&aring; sidste &aring;rs bronze plads skiftet ud med guld i &aring;r.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;"><span style="font-size:8.5pt;font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333;\r\nmso-fareast-language:DA;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA"> <span style="background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">Vi fors&oslash;gte at holde hum&oslash;ret h&oslash;jt blandt de uneg, trods den lokale arrangement-komittes beslutning om ikke at spille om point. Vi fik fortalt vores drenge, at det var vigtigere at deltage end at vinde. Heldigvis kunne de ikke helt&nbsp;forst&aring; dette og konkurrerede ivrigt mod de andre hold.&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">Og sportsligt&nbsp;klarede vi&nbsp;det ganske fremragende. Alle 5 kampe blev vundet sikkert med en fantastisk flot&nbsp;m&aring;lscore.&nbsp;Ja, der blev lavet s&aring; mange m&aring;l, at det var helt umuligt at holde m&aring;l-regnskabet ajour. For rigtig mange m&aring;l blev der scoret. Alle spillerne var s&aring;ledes meget stolte over den modtagne medalje samt erindringspokal, som nu st&aring;r i klubbens pokalskab.</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">Alt&nbsp;klappede -&nbsp;ogs&aring; den store medrejsende for&aelig;ldre-fan-gruppe. Og ikke mindst&nbsp;for arrang&oslash;rerne. Selv vejret&nbsp;var fantastisk&nbsp;p&aring; de 2 spilledage.&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">Endnu et superflot st&aelig;vne er&nbsp;gennemf&oslash;rt&nbsp;i 2015 med en fantastisk indsats fra vores norske br&oslash;dre:&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<b><span style="background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">Kol Hakavod og 1.000 tak&nbsp;</span></b><span style="background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">skal det lyde fra U8s drenge og deres meget tilfredse familier.&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">Tak til Hakoahs bestyrelse og&nbsp;ungdomsafdeling for at &quot;gide&quot; det store arbejde med at f&aring; alle detaljerne p&aring;&nbsp;plads.</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">Og ikke mindst&nbsp;tak til&nbsp;de mange&nbsp;familier, som g&oslash;r PGT til en uforglemmelig event og et vigtigt element i&nbsp;at styrke relationer og&nbsp;sammenhold blandt vores b&oslash;rn lokalt s&aring;vel som nordisk.</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size